OL,3,CMurder investigation after man dies
OL,4,Cfollowing assault in chip shop
OL,6,FA murder investigation has been
OL,7,Flaunched following the death of a 54-
OL,8,Fyear-old man who was attacked inside a
OL,9,Fchip shop.
OL,11,FThe assault reportedly took place at
OL,12,Fapproximately 7:30 pm on Friday, 17
OL,13,FApril, at The Village Chippy off Leach
OL,14,FCroft in Stockbridge Village on
OL,15,FMerseyside.
OL,17,FMerseyside Police confirmed the
OL,18,Fvictim, who has not been named, died
OL,19,Fin hospital four days later, after he
OL,20,Fwas admitted with a serious head
OL,21,Finjury.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
