OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1776848752
OL,3,CMurder investigation after man dies
OL,4,Cfollowing assault in chip shop
OL,6,FThe force says specialist officers are
OL,7,Fcurrently supporting his family and a
OL,8,Fpost-mortem examination is scheduled
OL,9,Fto formally establish his cause of
OL,10,Fdeath.
OL,12,FA 25-year-old man from Stockbridge
OL,13,FVillage was previously arrested on
OL,14,Fsuspicion of Section 18 wounding with
OL,15,Fintent. He remains on conditional bail
OL,16,Fas the investigation transitions into
OL,17,Fa murder inquiry.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
