PN,39303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1776848752
OL,3,CMurder investigation after man dies
OL,4,Cfollowing assault in chip shop
OL,6,FDetective Chief Inspector Cath
OL,7,FCummings said: "First and foremost,
OL,8,Four thoughts are with the man's family
OL,9,Fand friends at this tragic time.
OL,11,F"I know people living in the local
OL,12,Fcommunity will be understandably upset
OL,13,Fand concerned, but I want them to be
OL,14,Freassured that we are thoroughly
OL,15,Finvestigating the circumstances
OL,16,Fsurrounding this incident.
OL,18,F"We know there were people inside The
OL,19,FVillage Chippy at the time, so if you
OL,20,Fhaven't already done so, please come
OL,21,Fforward if you have information."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/3
